Titolo: Captain Goodnight and the Islands of Fear

Anno: 1985

Descrizione: Captain Goodnight and the Islands of Fear is a 1985 action video game by Broderbund. It was released on the Apple II, in English and French. The player must traverse air, sea and land in jets, jeeps, tanks, trams, boats, submarines, and on foot to advance toward enemy territory, the goal being deactivating the Doomsday Device on Doom Island. Along the way, enemy forces attempt to stop the captain.